=== 2011–12: ''Rabbits on the Run'' and ''Hear the Bells'' ===
[[File:Vanessa_Carlton_2011.jpg|right]]
卡尔顿的第四章录音室专辑《Rabbits on the Run》于2011年7月26日发行。发行该专辑的唱片公司Razor & Tie是她签约的第三个唱片公司<ref>{{cite web|url = http://www.razorandtie.com/news/vanessa-carlton-signs-razor-tie|title = vanessa carlton signs razor tie | Razor & Tie|publisher = Razorandtie.com|date = |accessdate = March 28, 2012|deadurl = yes|archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120323093351/http://razorandtie.com/news/vanessa-carlton-signs-razor-tie|archivedate = 2012年3月23日}}</ref> 。录制这张专辑之前，卡尔顿并不确定是要继续录制专辑，或是转而从事电影配乐<ref name="aolradioblog">{{cite web|author = Amar Toor|url = http://www.aolradioblog.com/new-album/vanessa-carlton-rabbits-on-the-run-2011/|title = Vanessa Carlton, 'Rabbits on the Run' – 2011 New Album Preview|publisher = Aol radiodate=2011-03-10|accessdate = February 4, 2013|archive-date = 2015-07-14|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150714042955/http://www.aolradioblog.com/new-album/vanessa-carlton-rabbits-on-the-run-2011/|dead-url = no}}</ref> 。决定再次尝试之后，她决定要在理想的环境里录制唱片，因而选择了位于英国的{{le|Real World Studios|Real World Studios}}。专辑名称中的“兔子”往往象征着时间流逝、思绪朦胧，正是她过去几年的内心写照 <ref name="facebook1">{{cite web|url = http://www.facebook.com/?ref=logo#!/notes/vanessa-carlton/update-on-the-new-record-and-my-epic-dog-tale/390921823302|title = Niet compatibele browser|publisher = Facebook|date = |accessdate = July 26, 2010|archive-date = 2015-07-04|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150704163807/https://www.facebook.com/?ref=logo#!/notes/vanessa-carlton/update-on-the-new-record-and-my-epic-dog-tale/390921823302|dead-url = no}}</ref> 。该专辑还受到了[[史蒂芬·霍金|史蒂芬·霍金]]的《[[时间简史|时间简史]]》和[[理查德·亚当斯|理查德·亚当斯]]的《[[瓦特希普高原|瓦特希普高原]]》两部书的启发。专辑中如梦幻般的声音归功于制作人Steve Osborne以及录音时直接录制在[[磁带|磁带]]上<ref name="aolradioblog">{{cite web|author = Amar Toor|url = http://www.aolradioblog.com/new-album/vanessa-carlton-rabbits-on-the-run-2011/|title = Vanessa Carlton, 'Rabbits on the Run' – 2011 New Album Preview|publisher = Aol radiodate=2011-03-10|accessdate = February 4, 2013}}</ref> 。5月3日第一首单曲《Carousel》 发布<ref>{{cite web|url = http://www.amazon.com/dp/B004XES56A|title = Carousel: Vanessa Carlton: MP3 Downloads|publisher = Amazon.com|date = |accessdate = May 9, 2011}}</ref> 。9月19日，她的经纪公司通过她的[[推特|推特]]宣布《I Don't Want to Be a Bride》将会是下一首单曲。卡尔顿又通过推特表示，唱片公司不会为《I Don't Want to Be a Bride》而是《Hear the Bells》制作[[音乐录影带|音乐录影带]]<ref>{{cite web|url = https://twitter.com/#!/vanessacarlton|title = Vanessa Carlton Twitter|publisher = Twitter.com|date = |accessdate = February 10, 2012|archive-date = 2016-11-03|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20161103181657/https://twitter.com/notch/status/192755231275229185#!/vanessacarlton|dead-url = no}}</ref> 。卡尔顿表示《Hear the Bells》是她目前为止最吐露真情的MV。该MV于2012年7月发行。

2011年11月10日，卡尔顿的经纪公司通过她的推特宣布即将发行一张圣诞主题[[迷你專輯|迷你专辑]]《<span>Hear the Bells》</span><ref>{{cite web|url = http://www.muenmagazine.net/2011/11/vanessa-carlton-to-release-new-digital-ep-hear-the-bells-on-november-21st/|title = Vanessa Carlton to release new EP, Hear the Bells, on November 21st|publisher = muenmagazine.com|date = |accessdate = November 11, 2011|deadurl = yes|archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20111112124402/http://www.muenmagazine.net/2011/11/vanessa-carlton-to-release-new-digital-ep-hear-the-bells-on-november-21st/|archivedate = 2011年11月12日}}</ref>。专辑包含4首歌，其中两首为原声版的《<span>Hear the Bells》和</span>《<span>A Thousand Miles</span>》。<ref>{{cite web|url = http://www.amazon.com/gp/product/B0064Y4Y08/|title = Hear The Bells EP: Vanessa Carlton: MP3 Downloads|publisher = Amazon.com|date = |accessdate = November 11, 2011}}</ref>

